Title: XL Plus Tattoo Design Deposit
Body (HTML):
Thank you for your business.  Custom Tattoo Design takes our extra large design deposits very seriously.  Our artist are tiered from 1-5 stars based on experience and performance; only our Sr. Design team work on these products so we can ensure top quality.  XL designs can take over 75+ hours to complete and may take 4-7 days to start your design depending on Sr artists availability. 

Thank you for your time and trust, we look forward to working with you soon. 

If you have any questions or concerns please contact our customer service manager Kaite @ 

Katie@customtattoodesign.ca

Title: Custom Tattoo Design : Gift Card
Body (HTML):
Finally an amazing unique gift idea ! 

Let us work with your family or friends to design a remarkable tattoo that will last forever! 

 Please select a denomination from the drop down menu.  Once you purchase your gift card it will be instantly delivered to you via email. The email will contain instructions on how your loved one can redeem the gift card when there ready to start there custom tattoo design. Our gift cards have no additional processing fees.  Should the balance of the design exceed the amount of the gift card, the customer will only be charged the balance. 

If you have any questions regarding gift cards please contact our customer service manager@

katie@customtattoodesign.ca
